---
title: Gnocchi with Chicken & Bacon plus Spinach in a Sun-Dried Tomato Cream Sauce
description: Ready for a dish that hits every craveable high note? Welcome this star to the stage—it's creamy, smoky, rich, bacony, and packed full of tender chicken and fluffy little gnocchi pillows. Sun-dried tomatoes, onion, garlic, and spinach add delicious depth to the savory sauce. A handful of Parm and more bacon on top will have you singing for your supper.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/gnocchi-with-chicken-bacon-9eb8a082.jpg
